item.title: Robotarium Intro
item.description: Robotarium is a free multi-agents robots hardware platform launched by Prof. Magnus Egerstedt’s lab from GaTech. It is developed by the intention of bringing the multi-agent hardware platform accessible to everyone, as maintaining it is expensive and not everyone can afford it.
